## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="29357-102">自訂的語音合成引擎定義類型的事件提交至語音平台合成器基礎結構與<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-102">Custom speech synthesis engines define the types of events submitted to the Speech platform synthesizer infrastructure with the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="29357-103">藉由設定執行規格<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A>屬性<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>執行個體會傳遞至<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A>類別實作的成員<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>介面傳遞到<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A>上自訂語音引擎的方法實作<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-103">Specification is performed by setting the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> property of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instances passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> member of the class implementing the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> method on a custom speech engine's implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="29357-104">語音平台基礎結構表示的目前透過處理的事件類型<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>屬性<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>傳遞至 speak 實作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-104">The Speech platform infrastructure indicates the type of events it is currently handling through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> passed to the speak implementation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="29357-105">值<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>的位元遮罩，其中的成員<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>定義事件類型對應的位元的位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-105">The value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> is a bitmask, where the members of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> define the location of the bit corresponding to the event type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29357-106">例如，WordBoundary 具有值為五 （5），這表示所傳回的值中的第五個位元<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>指示站台是否支援事件類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-106">For example, WordBoundary has a value of five (5), meaning the fifth bit in the value returned by <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> indicates if the site supports the event type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="29357-107">下列範例是繼承自自訂語音合成器實作的一部分<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>，並使用使用<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>， <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>， <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>，和 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-107">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="29357-108">實作 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-108">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="29357-109">接收的陣列<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>執行個體，並建立新的陣列<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>執行個體傳遞給`Speak`基礎的合成引擎上的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-109">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
2.  <span data-ttu-id="29357-110">如果<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>列舉值的中找到<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A>屬性<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A>傳回<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A>每個屬性<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A>執行個體是<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>，實作</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-110">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> enumeration value by found from the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property of each <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> instance is <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, the implementation</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="29357-111">將 Americanism Britishisms 以轉譯要讀出的文字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-111">Translates Americanism to Britishisms in the text to be spoken.</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="29357-112">如果<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>屬性<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>支援 WordBoundary 事件類型，提供給實作的介面<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>執行個體用來建立事件，以便建立合成器完成百分比的磁碟機。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-112">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> interfaces provided to the implementation support the WordBoundary event type, a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instance is used to create an event to drive a synthesizer progress meter is created.</span></span>  
  
3.  <span data-ttu-id="29357-113">語音轉譯引擎接著會呼叫以修改<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>陣列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29357-113">A speech rendering engine is then called with the modified <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> array.</span></span>  
  
```  
private const int WordBoundaryFlag = 1 << (int)TtsEventId.WordBoundary;  
private readonly char[] spaces = new char[] { ' ', '\t', '\r', '\n' };  
internal struct UsVsUk  
{  
  internal string UK;  
  internal string US;  
}  
  
override public void Speak (TextFragment [] frags, IntPtr wfx, ITtsEngineSite site)  
{  
  TextFragment [] newFrags=new TextFragment[frags.Length];  
  
  for (int i=0;i<frags.Length;i++){  
    newFrags[i].State=frags[i].State;  
    //truncate  
    newFrags[i].TextToSpeak = frags[i].TextToSpeak.Substring(frags[i].TextOffset,  
                               frags[i].TextLength);  
    newFrags[i].TextLength = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Length;  
    newFrags[i].TextOffset = 0;  
    if (newFrags[i].State.Action == TtsEngineAction.Speak) {  
      //Us to UK conversion  
      foreach (UsVsUk term in TransList) {  
      newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Replace(term.US, term.UK);  
      }  
      //Generate progress meter events if supported  
      if ((site.EventInterest & WordBoundaryFlag) != 0) {  
      string[] subs = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Split(spaces);  
  
      foreach (string s in subs) {  
        int offset = newFrags[i].TextOffset;  
        SpeechEventInfo spEvent = new SpeechEventInfo((Int16)TtsEventId.WordBoundary,   
                (Int16)EventParameterType.Undefined,   
                 s.Length, new IntPtr(offset));  
        offset += s.Length;  
        if (s.Trim().Length > 0) {  
          SpeechEventInfo[] events = new SpeechEventInfo[1];  
          events[0] = spEvent;  
          site.AddEvents(events, 1);  
        }  
      }  
      }  
    }  
  }  
  
  _baseSynthesize.Speak(newFrags, wfx, site);  
  
}  
```
